Detailed Description

This file contains MCAN sample code.

MCAN operational mode is set to CAN-FD. This test will need two MCAN nodes present two different EVM connected to each other.. Arbitration bit-rate and data phase bit-rate is set to 1Mbit/s and 5Mbit/s receptively.
